<sect1 id="keyboard-shortcuts">
<title>Keyboard Shortcuts</title>
<subtitle>Build a better Mousetrap</subtitle>
<para>While a mouse or other <quote>pointing device</quote> is a wonderfull thing the simple fact is that many operations 
on most Graphical User Interfaces can be undertaken much more efffectively using  Accelerators  
or Keyboard Shortcuts. While they are not as intuitive for most of us once learn't you wonder how you lived without them.</para>
<para>&app; is no exception to this &lt;pun&gt; rule_ of _thumb &lt;/pun&gt;. </para>
